To request an account deletion or data deletion from the Unity Cloud Service integrated with IdleTale, please send an e-mail to the email address stated at the bottom of this document including your Player ID
(found in the Settings menu inside the game after logging in).

The deleted data can be either the player's saved data only or the player's whole account, which deletes everything from the registry, including the player's saved data in the cloud.

In order to request an account deletion, send an e-mail to the address newageartsmail@gmail.com stating which data you'd like to be deleted.
